text: Komsomolsky () is a rural locality (a selo) in Duvansky Selsoviet, Duvansky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 52 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 72 km from Mesyagutovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Duvansky District
title: Komsomolsky, Duvansky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
